;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502032101: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G43/Act/Act_502032101.json-->
::'''Jingyan:''' One second.
::'''Jingyan:''' Alright. I'm Jingyan from the Realm-Keeping Commission, and I'm in charge of general affairs here. Is there anything that I can help you with?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What can you help me with?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502032104-->
:::'''Jingyan:''' ...I was just asking you that, but you asked me the same thing. Okay.
:::'''Jingyan:''' Household registrations, applications, and maintenance for local Xianzhou citizens. Handling of cases such as fighting, wounding with a weapon, theft, robbery. Processing census data, demographic statistics, resource allocation...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I get it. Please stop this monotonous chanting.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502032107-->
::::'''Jingyan:''' Looks like you aren't really that interested in the work of Realm-Keeping Commission officers.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Yes, you've all done a great job.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502032109-->
::::'''Jingyan:''' Ah, so you're here to inspect our work then? Thank you for taking the time to visit our humble Realm-Keeping Commission Chancery.
::::'''Jingyan:''' But I'm afraid it's currently during business hours, so please do not interrupt our everyday consultations.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502032121-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I've been cyber-scammed!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502032112-->
:::'''Jingyan:''' Cyber-scammed? We don't differentiate between scams happening online or offline here.
:::'''Jingyan:''' Please register your contact details, how the scammer contacted you, how you were scammed, and how much you were scammed out of? Go fill this out, and I'll verify your account for you.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Actually, I wasn't scammed at all.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502032115-->
::::'''Jingyan:''' Hmm. It's still currently during business hours, so please do not cause any trouble for our busy officers.
::::'''Jingyan:''' Based on my experience, you don't really look like a victim of scamming.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Th&mdash;There's no transaction record on the account.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502032118-->
::::'''Jingyan:''' This is a bit of a hassle. Not even the Realm-Keeping Commission can get back your "money that wasn't scammed."
::::'''Jingyan:''' Seems like you'll have to sort that part out on your own. Our hands are tied here at the Realm-Keeping Commission.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502032121-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I don't think I have anything that's connected to general affairs.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502032121-->
::'''Jingyan:''' Excuse me, do you have anything else?
